<body style="padding-left: 0rem;">
  <!-- SIDEBAR START -->
  <%- include("../template/sidebar.ejs") %>
    <!-- SIDEBAR END -->


    <!-- CONTAINER START -->
    <div class="container article-clean  py-2">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-10 col-xl-8 offset-lg-1 offset-xl-2">
          <div class="text-center intro">
            <h1 class="text-center">My Dreams</h1>
            <p class="text-center"><span class="by">by</span> <a href="#">Ruh Adam</a><span class="date">
              July 31<sup>th</sup> 2023
              </span></p>
          </div>
          <hr class="custom-hr">
          <div class="gif-container">
            <img src="/assets/videos/giphy.gif" style="width: 100px;" alt="gif" class="animated-gif">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
         
          <article class="postcard light blue" data-aos="fade-up"  data-aos-duration="1500">
            <a class="postcard__img_link" href="#">
              <img class="postcard__img" src="/assets/img/nyc2.jpg" alt="Image Title" />
            </a>
            <div class="postcard__text t-dark">
              <h1 class="postcard__title blue"><a href="#">New York</a></h1>
              <div class="postcard__subtitle small">
                <time datetime="2023-07-31 18:00:00">
                  <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt mr-2"></i>July 31 <sup>th</sup> 2023
                </time>
              </div>
              <div class="postcard__bar"></div>
              <div class="postcard__preview-txt">I don't know since when, but I've always wanted to see New York. However, I feel like my soul belongs there. I want to wander its streets, climb a skyscraper, and watch the cityscape. Unlike many people, I'm not fond of natural things. Skyscrapers and buildings are more interesting to me :)</div>
           
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="postcard light red" data-aos="fade-up"  data-aos-duration="1500">
            <a class="postcard__img_link" href="#">
              <img class="postcard__img" src="/assets/img/amg.png" alt="Image Title" />	
            </a>
            <div class="postcard__text t-dark">
              <h1 class="postcard__title red"><a href="#">Mercedes Benz</a></h1>
              <div class="postcard__subtitle small">
                <time datetime="2023-07-31 18:00:00">
                  <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt mr-2"></i>July 31 <sup>th</sup> 2023
                </time>
              </div>
              <div class="postcard__bar"></div>
              <div class="postcard__preview-txt">I'm sure everyone has a dream car they've always envisioned. Since childhood, the cars I've been a fan of are Mercedes. They are not only very stylish but also powerful and incredibly comfortable. That's why my preference leans towards Mercedes. Of course, there are many models to choose from, making the decision quite challenging. However, I think, even if I had billions, the car I would drive is the AMG GT63.</div>
        
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="postcard light green" data-aos="fade-up"  data-aos-duration="1500">
            <a class="postcard__img_link" href="#">
              <img class="postcard__img" src="/assets/img/setup.png" alt="Image Title" />
            </a>
            <div class="postcard__text t-dark">
              <h1 class="postcard__title green"><a href="#">Perfect Setup</a></h1>
              <div class="postcard__subtitle small">
                <time datetime="2023-07-31 18:00:00">
                  <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt mr-2"></i>July 31 <sup>th</sup> 2023
                </time>
              </div>
              <div class="postcard__bar"></div>
              <div class="postcard__preview-txt">I started using computers at a very young age, around 4 or 5 years old, I believe. I have been using computers for a long time now. Anyone involved with computers wishes to have a good computer and equipment. My passion for computers helped me choose my profession, and I continue my life as a web developer. Having my workspace at maximum comfort is among my dreams. Additionally, I want a minibar under my desk. I can open it whenever I want and grab a cold drink.</div>
           
            </div>
          </article>
         
        </div>
      
   

